unwilling host
Discworld ritual help
unwilling host

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Unwilling host - Sets up a spiritual tap with which you can draw energy from your victim.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Unwilling host is an offensive ritual, which infects your victim with divine parasites.  These unexpected guests will set up a spiritual link between you and your victim allowing you to tap power from them with other rituals.  To perform this ritual you will need a holy symbol of your god.
.EP
